Left click select
num pads - 1 3 7 9 - views
num pad . - focus
x - delete
s - scale 
r - rotate


Tab - edit mode
Cntl-tab - select menu 

e - extrude
cntl + r - split/ use scroll wheel to multiply
f - fill in 
a - select all
l - select island
shift+d - duplicate

cntl+j - link together
p - separate

shift+tab - snap mode

o - edit selected